item.title: [HBASE-14466] Remove duplicated code from MOB snapshot tests
item.description: mob snapshots tests are just a copy paste of the base test with a different createTable to include mobs. remove the duplicated code and extend the base tests
item.summary: Remove duplicated code from MOB snapshot tests

status.description: A resolution has been taken, and it is awaiting verification by reporter. From here issues are either reopened, or are closed.

comments.comment:
found a bug with TestMobSnapshotCloneIndependence.. forgot to call the correct load data.
but basically all the changes are:

  • extend the mob test class from the snapshot base one
  • make create/countRow pluggable and implement the mob version
  • remove all the tests from the mob class
